---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Data Connectivity & Visibility | Intelio - One Source of Truth" description="One source of truth. Real-time dashboards. All your fragmented data unified so leadership sees current state and makes confident decisions.">
<main class="bg-white">
  <!-- SECTION 1: HERO -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden bg-black">
    <!-- Video Background -->
    <video 
      autoplay
      muted
      loop
      playsinline
      preload="auto"
      webkit-playsinline="true"
      x5-playsinline="true"
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
      style="min-width: 100%; min-height: 100%; width: auto; height: auto;"
    >
      <source src="/videos/system-integration-hero.mp4" type="video/mp4">
      Your browser does not support the video tag.
    </video>
    
    <!-- Dark Overlay for Text Readability -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/55 z-[1]"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 w-full">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <!-- Label -->
        <div class="mb-6">
          <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">
            DATA CONNECTIVITY & VISIBILITY
          </span>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Headline -->
        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl text-white leading-[1.1] mb-6 tracking-tight">
          One Source of Truth. Real-Time Visibility.
        </h1>
        
        <!-- Subhead -->
        <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-gray-200 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          All your fragmented data unified in real-time dashboards. Leadership sees current state. Decisions made with confidence instead of guesses.
        </p>
        
        <!-- CTA Button -->
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white text-lg font-semibold rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-200 ease-out">
          Start a Project
          <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 2: INTRO -->
  <section class="py-32 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-gray-900 mb-8">
        Unify Your Data. See Everything in Real-Time.
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Your data is fragmented across systems. Nobody sees the whole picture. Reporting is manual. Dashboards are stale. Decisions are made on incomplete information.
        </p>
        <p>
          Intelio builds data connectivity systems that unify all your fragmented data in real-time dashboards. One source of truth everyone trusts. Leadership sees current state. Decisions made with confidence.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-600">
        <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
          This isn't consulting. This isn't advice. It's infrastructure.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 3: WHAT'S BROKEN & WHAT CHANGES (SIDE BY SIDE) -->
  <section class="py-32 px-6 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-20 relative">
        <!-- Vertical Divider Line -->
        <div class="hidden md:block absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-black transform -translate-x-1/2"></div>
        
        <!-- Left Column: What's Broken Today -->
        <div class="relative">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-gray-900 mb-12">What's Broken Today</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <!-- Card 1 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 ease-out">
              <h3 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Fragmented Data Across Systems</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Customer data in CRM, financial data in accounting, operational data in project management. Nobody sees the whole picture. Decisions made on partial information.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 2 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 ease-out">
              <h3 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Manual Monthly Reporting</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Finance spends 2-3 days compiling monthly reports (exporting from multiple systems, reconciling differences). By the time the report is done, the data is stale.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 3 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 ease-out">
              <h3 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Stale Dashboards</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Your dashboard updated yesterday shows today's situation was already obsolete. Problems not caught until monthly close. Opportunities missed because trends weren't visible.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 4 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 ease-out">
              <h3 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Conflicting Information</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Finance sees one version of customer data; operations sees another. Different departments make decisions based on conflicting information. Arguments about "what's really true?"
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Column: What Changes After Deployment -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-gray-900 mb-12">What Changes After Deployment</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <!-- Card 1 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 ease-out">
              <h3 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Single Source of Truth</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                All departments see same data. CRM, accounting, operations all show same customer record, same deal status, same project status. No conflicts. No arguments about "what's really true?"
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 2 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 ease-out">
              <h3 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Real-Time Data Flow</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Data flows automatically from source systems continuously. Dashboards update as information changes, not at end of day. Minutes not hours behind reality.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 3 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 ease-out">
              <h3 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Instant Reporting</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                No manual compilation. Reports pull from live data, generate in seconds, not days. Finance team analyzes instead of compiling. Time freed for strategic thinking.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 4 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 ease-out">
              <h3 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Early Warning System</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                System continuously monitors and surfaces issues automatically. Project margin trending down? Alert sent before it's a crisis. Customer engagement declining? Detected before churn.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 5 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 ease-out">
              <h3 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Confident Decision-Making</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Leaders see current, accurate information. No guessing. No conflicting data. Decisions made with confidence based on knowledge, not assumptions or incomplete information.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 5: HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section class="py-32 px-6 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-gray-900 mb-12">How the System Actually Works</h2>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Continuous Data Capture</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Data exists in your systems (CRM, accounting, project management, HR, operations). The visibility system continuously detects every change: new record, updated record, status change. Nothing is missed.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Standardization & Validation</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Formats differ across systems (customer ID in CRM is different than accounting). The system normalizes everything so it connects properly. Deduplicates (same customer in two places becomes one). Validates for quality before problems emerge.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Analytics & Monitoring</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Data is organized for answering business questions. Dimensional schemas let you slice and dice by customer, by service, by time period. Business metrics are calculated (margin, cash position, customer acquisition cost). The system watches for patterns and issues, sending alerts when attention is needed.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Real-Time Dashboards</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Users see current, accurate information. Executive dashboards show business health. Departmental dashboards show finance P&L, operations delivery, sales pipeline. Detailed reports for analysis. Ad-hoc query tools so business users can ask questions without IT.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 6: THIS ACTUALLY WORKS -->
  <section class="py-32 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-gray-900 mb-12">This Actually Works</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-12 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
        These visibility systems are providing real-time insights to leadership and operations teams right now.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-4xl text-blue-600 mb-2 font-bold">10-50</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-900 mb-4 font-semibold">Data connections per client</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            CRM, accounting, project management, HR, operations. All feeding real-time dashboards.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-4xl text-blue-600 mb-2 font-bold">50,000-500,000</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-900 mb-4 font-semibold">Data events processed per day</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            New records, updates, status changes. All flowing continuously into analytics layer.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-4xl text-blue-600 mb-2 font-bold">&lt; 5 minutes</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-900 mb-4 font-semibold">Dashboard update latency</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            Most data real-time. Some daily. Transparent about what's live vs. batched.
