        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-4xl text-blue-600 mb-2 font-bold">99.5%+</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-900 mb-4 font-semibold">System uptime</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            Running continuously for 6+ months. Redundancy built in for critical data flows.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Time Saved</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-blue-600 text-xl mt-1">•</span>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Financial reporting: 40 hours manual compilation → 15 minutes automated</p>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-blue-600 text-xl mt-1">•</span>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Profitability analysis: Ad-hoc 2-3 day requests → instant self-service</p>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-blue-600 text-xl mt-1">•</span>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Dashboard updates: Manual monthly rebuild → automated continuous</p>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-blue-600 text-xl mt-1">•</span>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Exception detection: Manual weekly reviews → automatic continuous</p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Decision Speed Improvement</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-blue-600 text-xl mt-1">•</span>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Margin problem detection: 1 month → 1 day</p>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-blue-600 text-xl mt-1">•</span>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Churn risk detection: After churn → 2 weeks early</p>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-blue-600 text-xl mt-1">•</span>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Improvement opportunities: Quarterly review → continuous visibility</p>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-blue-600 text-xl mt-1">•</span>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Financial close: 5-7 days → 2-3 days</p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Pattern Discovery in Action</h3>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-600 mb-6">
          These dashboards surface patterns leadership didn't see before.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-blue-600 text-xl mt-1">•</span>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Discovered certain customer types have 3x profitability (now targeting those types)</p>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-blue-600 text-xl mt-1">•</span>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Found projects over 6 months have 40% margin slip (now implementing controls)</p>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-blue-600 text-xl mt-1">•</span>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Identified customer acquisition cost varies 2x by source (now optimizing channels)</p>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-blue-600 text-xl mt-1">•</span>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Surfaced team A delivers 2x faster than team B (now understanding why and scaling)</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 7: ENGAGEMENT MODELS -->
  <section class="py-32 px-6 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-gray-900 mb-12">Engagement Models</h2>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Card 1: Build + Maintain -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-2">Build + Maintain</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6">You own the dashboards. We maintain the infrastructure.</p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">You Own</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">What questions you ask, what dashboards you need, how you use the data</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">We Own</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Data pipeline health, accuracy, infrastructure performance, system changes</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Best For</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">You have a business analyst or data person who can define dashboards. You want strategic oversight with hands-on involvement.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Pricing</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Project fee + monthly maintenance</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2: Build + Operate -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-2">Build + Operate</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6">We own the entire visibility system.</p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">You Own</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Business outcomes and strategy. Using dashboards for decisions.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">We Own</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Data pipelines, dashboards, reporting, optimization, insights</p>
            </div>
            <div>
