              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">You want visibility to "just work." You need someone accountable for data quality and insights.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Pricing</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Monthly operating retainer</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-6">What's Always Clear</h3>
