  <!-- SECTION 8: COMMON DASHBOARDS -->
  <section class="py-32 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-gray-900 mb-12">Common Dashboards We Build</h2>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Revenue & Forecast Dashboard</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">WHAT YOU SEE</p>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Deal pipeline by stage and amount. Historical conversion rates. Revenue forecast (realistic, not inflated). Cash flow projection based on deal timing and payment terms. Revenue trend month-over-month and year-over-year.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-4 border-l-4 border-blue-600">
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">DECISIONS IT ENABLES</p>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-900">How much revenue can we realistically expect? What's our cash runway? Where should sales focus? Is the business healthy?</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
