          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">WHAT YOU SEE</p>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Profit by customer (revenue minus delivery cost). Profit by service/product (which is most profitable?). Profit by project (is this making money?). Profit by team (productivity differences?). Margin trend (improving or declining?).</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-4 border-l-4 border-blue-600">
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">DECISIONS IT ENABLES</p>
