              <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Current cash position. Cash flow projection (inflows and outflows). Runway calculation (months of cash remaining). Expense trends (are costs growing faster than revenue?). Working capital (accounts receivable and payable).</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-4 border-l-4 border-blue-600">
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">DECISIONS IT ENABLES</p>
