              <p class="text-base text-gray-900">Can we take on new projects? Are we going to deliver on time? Is this project profitable? How can we improve delivery?</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
